parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience issues with the airbags, leading to potential accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls
loses power
experiences issues with the airbags
and has difficulty starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience issues with starting, leading to potential accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: The key fails to open the door
fails to turn in the ignition
and the vehicle has difficulty starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to potential accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: The brake pedal travels to the floor without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel can cause the driver to lose visibility of important gauges and indicators, leading to potential accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: The instrument panel does not light up
and the vanity lights
interior overhead lights
and universal garage door opener do not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion and Failure of Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS) Valve Stems
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion and failure of TPMS valve stems can cause sudden and complete loss of tire pressure, leading to accidents, loss of control, and potential fatalities.
symptoms: Tire pressure warning light illuminates
sudden loss of tire pressure
flat tires
corroded or broken valve stems
and failure of TPMS sensors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of steering control, making it difficult or impossible to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels hard to turn
the steering wheel locks up
the vehicle sways side to side when hitting a bump or pothole
the vehicle is difficult to control
the steering system fails to respond.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause loss of power, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts off while driving
the vehicle loses power
the steering wheel locks up
the brakes are difficult to use
the vehicle is difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various malfunctions, including engine stalling, power steering failure, and loss of control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
